Goal: use Terraform module

Infrastructure as service (IaaS): {AWS, AZURE, Google Cloud} ==> primitives
Platform as service (PaaS): {Heroku, Docker Cloud, Engine Yard} ==> higher api for deploying app
PaaS limitation: scale, customize


